    • createNewPrescription

      public Prescription createNewPrescription(LoggedInInfo info, List<Drug> drugs, Integer demographicNo)
      Creates a new prescription object and persists a copy of it in the database. Does not update/change any of the Drug objects that are passed in.
      Specified by:
      createNewPrescription in interface PrescriptionManager
      Parameters:
      info - regarding the current user/session.
      drugs - that are associated with this prescription.
      demographicNo - the demographic this prescription is for.
      Returns:
      the Prescription object that was created.
      Throws:
      AccessDeniedException - if the user is not allowed to write to the demographic's record.
